      'Extreme political polarization post-January 8 insurrection with Bolsonaro movement remaining powerful',
      'Supreme Court activism raising questions about judicial overreach versus defending democracy',
      'Security crisis with drug trafficking organizations controlling territories and high homicide rates',
      'Fiscal constraints limiting social spending amid high public debt and inflation pressures',
      'Corruption endemic across institutions despite Lava Jato investigation revealing systemic malfeasance'
